OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,FKevin Healey tells ITV Central's Rosie
OL,7,FDowsing about the daily struggles he
OL,8,Ffaces trying to get access to ADHD
OL,9,Ftreatment.
OL,11,FA man from who got a private diagnosis
OL,12,Ffor says he has been told if he wants
OL,13,FNHS treatment, he needs to wait at
OL,14,Fleast a year for an NHS assessment.
OL,16,FKevin Healey, an autism campaigner
OL,17,Ffrom , paid #2,000 for his private
OL,18,FADHD assessment with top doctor Dr
OL,19,FCarol Stott. He says the process was
OL,20,Fthorough and robust, lasting 20 hours.
