OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,FBut in February, Kevin was told by the
OL,7,Fthat regardless of his private
OL,8,Fdiagnosis, he would need to be re-
OL,9,Fassessed if he wanted to access NHS
OL,10,Ftreatment - which could take over a
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FAttention deficit hyperactivity
OL,14,Fdisorder (ADHD) is a condition that
OL,15,Faffects people's behaviour and
OL,16,Fconcentration.
OL,18,FKevin said it affects almost every
OL,19,Fdaily task: "the littlest thing can
OL,20,Fmake me frustrated, can cause huge
OL,21,Famounts of anxiety, and stress.
