OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,F"People are born with ADHD and autism,
OL,7,Fit's not a midlife crisis thing.
OL,9,F"My ADHD has never been picked up and
OL,10,Feven as a child my autism was never
OL,11,Fpicked up. So I struggled through
OL,12,Flife, through education too, with
OL,13,Fbullying."
OL,15,FThe 49-year-old autism campaigner said
OL,16,Fthe wait for an NHS re-assessment may
OL,17,Fnot even ensure he gets access to
OL,18,Fmedication, because his original
OL,19,Fdiagnosis could be revoked.
