OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,FThe letter Kevin received from his
OL,7,Flocal Adult ADHD Assessment Team said:
OL,9,F"We are aware that you already have a
OL,10,Fprivate diagnosis of ADHD, but after
OL,11,Freviewing the information provided
OL,12,Fabout your symptoms, it was felt that
OL,13,Fyou are suitable for further screening
OL,14,Ffor possible re-assessment.
OL,16,F"It's important to mention that re-
OL,17,Fassessment may result in a diagnosis
OL,18,Fof ADHD not being made and if this is
OL,19,Fthe case, your diagnosis will be
OL,20,Frevoked."
