OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,FThose working in the field say the
OL,7,Flonger waits for a diagnosis are
OL,8,Fbecause of a surge in demand on the
OL,9,FNHS following greater awareness of
OL,10,FADHD symptoms.
OL,12,FProfessor Amanda Kirby, ADHD
OL,13,Fspecialist and Chairperson of the ADHD
OL,14,FFoundation, said: "The secondary
OL,15,Fimpact of not being diagnosed has a
OL,16,Flong lasting impact on psychological
OL,17,Fwellbeing.
