OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,F"ADHD should be looked at like
OL,7,Fdiabetes - unless you identify and
OL,8,Fsupport somebody you'll see the
OL,9,Fsecondary consequences of untreated
OL,10,FADHD happening."
OL,12,FADHD UK predicts there are 1.9 million
OL,13,Fadults living in the UK with the
OL,14,Fcondition.
OL,16,FKevin said private treatment would be
OL,17,Funaffordable, and the uncertainty
OL,18,Fsurrounding whether he can access the
OL,19,FNHS is giving him anxiety.
