OL,3,CADHD: 'My private diagnosis cost me
OL,4,C#2,000 but could be revoked by the NHS'
OL,6,FHe said: "If I can't get the diagnosis
OL,7,Fon the NHS then I would have to see a
OL,8,Fprivate psychiatrist.
OL,10,F"In essence, it could cost me between
OL,11,F#200-400 a month, to see a
OL,12,Fpsychiatrist and obtain the
OL,13,Fmedication. I shouldn't have to pay
OL,14,Fthat.
OL,16,F"It's not just me, it's affecting so
OL,17,Fmany people in the region and
OL,18,Fnationally.
OL,20,F"I'm not prepared to wait, why should
OL,21,FI have to wait."
