OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said:
OL,9,F"We know it's vital to have a timely
OL,10,Fdiagnosis of ADHD, and we are taking
OL,11,Faction to reduce assessment delays.
OL,13,F"NHS England is establishing a new
OL,14,FADHD taskforce alongside the
OL,15,Fgovernment to improve care for people
OL,16,Fliving with the condition.
